org.pimslims.business.crystallization.model
Class PlateExperimentRequest

java.lang.Object
  org.pimslims.business.crystallization.model.PlateExperimentRequest

public class PlateExperimentRequest
    
extends java.lang.Object





Details about a plate experiment request


A request concern a sample (if same sample at different concentration
create another PlateExperimentRequest).


The sample have an owner, a contact, a desire run date, informations
about screens, safety...


Some of this request details can be modified or deleted by the owner (or
the admin).
